<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">

<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Sónia Guerra | Nettoyage Basel</title>
<meta name="description" content="Services professionnels de nettoyage et aide à domicile à Basel et alentours. Contact rapide par WhatsApp.">

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box;}
body{font-family:Poppins,sans-serif; color:#333; background:#fff; line-height:1.6;}
a{text-decoration:none; color:#333;}
.container{max-width:1200px; margin:auto; padding:20px;}

/* HEADER */
header{
text-align:center;
padding:40px 20px;
}
header img{width:120px; margin-bottom:15px;}
header h1{font-size:40px; color:#d4af37; margin-bottom:10px;}
header p{font-size:18px;}

/* SERVICES */
.services{padding:60px 20px; text-align:center;}
.services h2{font-size:32px; margin-bottom:40px; color:#d4af37;}
.grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr)); gap:25px;}
.card{padding:25px; border-radius:10px; box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); transition:0.3s; background:white;}
.card:hover{transform:translateY(-5px);}
.card h3{margin-bottom:10px; color:#c7a23a;}

/* ABOUT */
.about{padding:60px 20px; text-align:center; background:#f8f8f8;}
.about p{max-width:700px; margin:auto; font-size:18px;}

/* GALLERY */
.gallery{padding:60px 20px; text-align:center;}
.gallery h2{font-size:32px; margin-bottom:40px; color:#d4af37;}
.gallery-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr)); gap:15px;}
.gallery img{width:100%; border-radius:10px; transition:0.4s; cursor:pointer;}
.gallery img:hover{transform:scale(1.05);}

/* CONTACT */
.contact{padding:60px 20px; text-align:center; background:#fafafa;}
.contact h2{font-size:32px; margin-bottom:20px; color:#d4af37;}
.contact p{font-size:18px; margin:8px 0;}

/* WHATSAPP BUTTON */
.whatsapp{position:fixed; bottom:25px; right:25px; background:#25D366; color:white; padding:15px 22px; border-radius:50px; font-weight:600; box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);}
.whatsapp:hover{transform:scale(1.1); transition:0.3s;}

/* FOOTER */
footer{background:#111; color:white; text-align:center; padding:30px; margin-top:40px;}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<header>
<img src="logo.png" alt="Logo">
<h1>Sónia Guerra</h1>
<p>Aide à domicile – Nettoyage à Basel et alentours</p>
</header>

<section class="services">
<h2>Services</h2>
<div class="grid">
<div class="card"><h3>Nettoyage maisons</h3><p>Entretien complet et professionnel.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Appartements</h3><p>Service sérieux et discret.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Nettoyage profond</h3><p>Résultats impeccables.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Après déménagement</h3><p>Remise en état rapide.</p></div>
</div>
</section>

<section class="about">
<h2>À propos</h2>
<p>Je propose des services professionnels de nettoyage et aide à domicile à Basel et alentours. Travail sérieux, discret et professionnel pour maisons et appartements. Langues : Français / Portugais.</p>
</section>

<section class="gallery">
<h2>Galerie</h2>
<div class="gallery-grid">
<img src="photo1.jpg" alt="Nettoyage">
<img src="photo2.jpg" alt="Nettoyage">
<img src="photo3.jpg" alt="Nettoyage">
<img src="photo4.jpg" alt="Nettoyage">
</div>
</section>

<section class="contact">
<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>📧 soniaguerra15fr@gmail.com</p>
<p>📞 +33 6 82 63 22 39</p>
<p>📍 Basel et alentours</p>
</section>

<footer>
© Sónia Guerra – Nettoyage Basel
</footer>

<a class="whatsapp" href="https://wa.me/33682632239">WhatsApp</a>

</body>
</html>
